1. *Ros* se sakupio na listovima nakon kiše. (Dew* has gathered on the leaves after the rain.)
2. U rano jutro *rosa* pokriva travu. (In the early morning, *dew* covers the grass.)
3. Nekoliko *rosnih* kapljica sletelo je na moj prozor. (Several *dewy* drops landed on my window.)
4. Biljke su bile *okupane rosi* i izgledale su prekrasno. (The plants were *bathed in dew* and looked beautiful.)
5. Moramo obaviti posao prije nego što *ros* padne noćas. (We have to get the job done before *frost* falls tonight.)
6. *Rosom* natopljena trava izgledala je sjajno na jutarnjem suncu. (The grass *drenched with dew* looked amazing in the morning sun.)
7. *Rosa* na staklu otežava vidljivost. (The *frost* on the glass makes visibility difficult.)
8. Kupili smo novi *rosač* za zalijevanje biljaka. (We bought a new *watering can* for watering the plants.)